Isaiah 43-15 <t>I am the LORD, your Holy One, </t><t>the Creator of Israel, your King.” </t>
Isaiah 43-16 <pb/><t>Thus says the LORD, </t><t><f>ⓨ</f>who makes a way in the sea, </t><t>a path in the mighty waters,</t>
