Isaiah 43-18 <t><f>ⓒ</f> “Remember not the former things, </t><t>nor consider the things of old.</t>
Isaiah 43-19 <t><f>ⓓ</f> Behold, I am doing a new thing; </t><t>now it springs forth, do you not perceive it? </t><t><f>ⓔ</f>I will make a way in the wilderness </t><t><f>ⓕ</f>and rivers in the desert.</t>
