Isaiah 43-21 <t>the people whom I formed for myself </t><t><f>ⓘ</f>that they might declare my praise. </t>
Isaiah 43-22 <pb/><t>“Yet you did not call upon me, O Jacob; </t><t>but <f>ⓙ</f>you have been weary of me, O Israel!</t>
Isaiah 43-23 <t><f>ⓚ</f> You have not brought me your sheep for burnt offerings, </t><t>or honored me with your sacrifices. </t><t>I have not burdened you with offerings, </t><t><f>ⓛ</f>or wearied you with frankincense.</t>
